WorkItem.Description:
When I try to load my character on http://www.elitistjerks.com/rawr.php firefox and safari both lock up. I'm able to load a number of other characters, but for some reason only mine locks it up.
 
Steps to reproduce:
1) Launch rawr at elitist jerks
2) File > Load Character from Armory
3) US Realm Rexxar
4) Character Braelwulf
5) Observe
 
Additional Info:
Browser: Firefox and Safari
OS: Apple OS X Snow Leopard
WorkItem.Summary: [LoadCharacter] Browser Locks Up on My Character Only
